org.apache.freemarker.core

Class WrongTemplateCharsetException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.io.IOException
          • org.apache.freemarker.core.ParseException
            • org.apache.freemarker.core.WrongTemplateCharsetException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class WrongTemplateCharsetException
extends ParseException
    Thrown by the Template constructors that specify a non-null encoding whoch doesn't match the encoding specified in the #ftl header of the template.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
